title: NECKFACE for Altamont look book
description:
"The whole line is basically based off bum wine and stealing shit. Cheap booze and stealing shit to save your money to buy a new board. For skateboarders, that's nothing new to us. Stealing is part of our deals, we don't have a lot a money. Hopefully the kids will be able to get their stuff easier and quicker."

Music by Altamont contributor Zach Hill.
